T(n) =\sum_{j=2}^{n}\Theta(j) = \Theta(n^2) 
 \sum_{j=2}^{n}\Theta(j) = \frac{n(n-1)}2 - \frac{1(1 - 1)}{2} =  \frac{n(n-1)}2
 \frac{n^2-n}2 
 \frac{n^2-n}2 = \frac12n^2 - \frac12 n =  \Theta(n^2) 
n(n-1)/2
 \sum_{j=2}^n j = \left(\sum_{j=1}^n j\right)-1=\frac{n(n+1)}{2}-1=\frac{n^2+n-2}{2} 
